“Providence has wisely ordered that the more numerous men are, the more difficult it is for them to agree in anything, and so [ultimately triumphant non-communism, i.e. technocapital singularity].” -- Tweaked Samuel Johnson
(The untweaked version in more Yarvin.)
And yet it so vastly outperforms the median human already it's not even funny.
If you aren't aiming for Mars you end up like this.
... Faustian spirit completely off the rails.
Hideous Things you can do to your Anus, aka Postmodernism.
Closing in on the true Eden story.
The Satanic Tragedy is the great mystery. Secular-historical version:
'Atlantean Albion' gets the treasured Satanic endorsement.
Women went disastrously wrong in this millennium. No getting around it.
... Statistically inescapable that listening to women is a mistake.
... Of course, given the existence of anomalous cases, you might hear something wise, or at least sensible, but why take the risk?

Dear XX-chromosome fellow humans, you really need to understand that unless you rein-back the authoritarian hyper-empathy and social conformism very considerably, carbon-based life on this planet is probably going to have to go.
